{"tid":2357705,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男教師否認襲警 裁判官睇片認不出警員 裁判官稱：「梗係啦都無冧巴」","createTime":"2021-01-07T15:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T16:32:11.000Z","uid":48,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"04c7a86f464fc5ec7dbd2a926058b191fdf2e3b6","tid":2357705,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T15:14:37.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z4yfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=146fbe5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】2019年9月8日晚港島區多處有警民衝突，當晚一名27歲男教師涉嫌在港鐵銅鑼灣站外襲警被捕。他否認一項襲擊在正當執行職務之警務人員罪，案件今（7日）在東區法院開審。兩名作供警員均不能在呈堂錄影片段中認出同僚，裁判官鄧少雄見狀便稱：「梗係啦都無冧巴，梗係認唔到啦」。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告陳睿懿於2019年9月8日，在港鐵銅鑼灣站F1出口外襲擊在正當執行職務的警員趙金。<br />\n<br />\n警長林榕南供稱，當晚7時許銅鑼灣F出口外有數十人聚集，大叫「死黑警」等口號，當中包括被告。林認為被告的舉動或會破壞社會秩序，於是上前調查，惟當他伸手搭被告膊頭之時，被告突然轉身逃跑，他嘗試追上不過被膠欄絆倒，起來見被告已被制服。<br />\n<br />\n而報稱受襲的警員趙金供稱，當晚他見被告轉身逃跑，便追上捉住被告的上衣，之後二人失平衡雙雙倒地，他將被告壓住，惟被告不斷掙扎，更揮拳打了他的左臉一下。其後在同袍的協助下制服被告。趙事後送院接受治療，即晚出院。<br />\n<br />\n趙在庭上稱見到軍裝警想搭被告膊頭，但口供紙又寫是搭住了被告膊頭，遭到辯方質疑。趙回應說：「寫錯咗，我承認」，更承認自己「學歷低、寫得差、表達能力唔好」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">惟林、趙兩人均未能在呈堂片段中認出同僚，裁判官頗有微言，直指：「我點知邊個警員係邊個警員呀？」、「梗係啦都無冧巴，梗係認唔到啦」。</span></span></strong>趙回應覺得背部標記「條條揈、好論盡」，故此沒有有制服上展示警員編號。聆訊未完，2月10日續審。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%94%B7%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6-%E8%AD%A6%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E8%AA%8D%E5%87%BA%E5%90%8C%E8%A2%8D-%E5%AE%98-%E6%A2%97%E4%BF%82%E5%95%A6%E9%83%BD%E7%84%A1%E5%86%A7%E5%B7%B4-112723602.html?fbclid=IwAR3i0xDUvfzCJLoh5WavCLuahl9g50r9X5j1AtxB0CDTc7nWrI8tfoVY5Cw&amp;guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly9sLmZhY2Vib29rLmNvbS8&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAABfVoycUtvwR4vuPD3toMDbQcX75cpMFCayr081mp95HszauPP3XRhpZHXKCP1lO8MXsvJW3j1-a1M8p5slU2DrIv2t_Vd7LHx4B7qcka0cmXTGMm2rD4wgFb7PMtbr2kRN8LqpnVjkWGBE9pW5vxruoCG6KpcvQtu0cvZSPzwGC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%25A2%258D-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E6%25A2%2597%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2595%25A6%25E9%2583%25BD%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2586%25A7%25E5%25B7%25B4-112723602.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3i0xDUvfzCJLoh5WavCLuahl9g50r9X5j1AtxB0CDTc7nWrI8tfoVY5Cw%26guccounter%3D1%26guce_referrer%3DaHR0cHM6Ly9sLmZhY2Vib29rLmNvbS8%26guce_referrer_sig%3DAQAAABfVoycUtvwR4vuPD3toMDbQcX75cpMFCayr081mp95HszauPP3XRhpZHXKCP1lO8MXsvJW3j1-a1M8p5slU2DrIv2t_Vd7LHx4B7qcka0cmXTGMm2rD4wgFb7PMtbr2kRN8LqpnVjkWGBE9pW5vxruoCG6KpcvQtu0cvZSPzwGC&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z4yfatP4vaZW2FmQrzE7DSA%3D&h=1047fb4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%94%B7%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6-%E8%AD%A6%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E8%AA%8D%E5%87%BA%E5%90%8C%E8%A2%8D-%E5%AE%98-%E6%A2%97%E4%BF%82%E5%95%A6%E9%83%BD%E7%84%A1%E5%86%A7%E5%B7%B4-112723602.html?fbclid=IwAR3i0xDUvfzCJLoh5WavCLuahl9g50r9X5j1AtxB0CDTc7nWrI8tfoVY5Cw&amp;guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly9sLmZhY2Vib29rLmNvbS8&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAABfVoycUtvwR4vuPD3toMDbQcX75cpMFCayr081mp95HszauPP3XRhpZHXKCP1lO8MXsvJW3j1-a1M8p5slU2DrIv2t_Vd7LHx4B7qcka0cmXTGMm2rD4wgFb7PMtbr2kRN8LqpnVjkWGBE9pW5vxruoCG6KpcvQtu0cvZSPzwGC</a>"},{"pid":"64028717de22e1f0a97b3507cdcde3f7accc09cc","tid":2357705,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ba701adc7fe92543144346958bf031429e53cb","tid":2357705,"uid":335434,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T15:17:40.000Z","msg":"你條狗撚夠「條條揈、好論盡」啦 唔切柒咗佢落嚟放喺屋企收埋先出街<img src=\"/a